Want to bring a fleshed out Sandbox VR experience to your phone? Chicken Waffle has done a great job capturing the essence of innocence and exploration of childhood. It has the same feel as a Rugrats adventure, and definitely has kept the charm that the PCVR version brought to the table. Give it a try, you won't be disappointed!

Baby Hands Jr is a standout in a crowded marketplace! A unique idea that was an incredibly fun VR experience has been wonderfully recreated on mobile. After a couple of minutes of getting used to the controls, they become intuitive and combined with the theme of the game, deliver a fun and refreshing mobile game.
Brilliant, playful game with seriously good controls. Perfect implementation of the original VR, leaves nothing more to wish for!
